DISK MANAGEMENT COMMANDS
**********************************************************
1. Check the disk usage :

Shows the filesystem usage and avaliable spaces

 Command : df -h


2. Check the Directory Size

 Shows the total Directory size

 Command : df -sh

 Example : df -sh /var/log


3.View BLock Devices

 List all disk and paritions

  Command : lsblk

4.Display Partition Information

 Displays detailed information about all disks and their partitions.

  Command : fdisk -l 